reviewText: Nothing Beats 1 hour of soft piano music accompanying 150 pure Caucasian baby faces full of drool. Want to watch a completely color blind film set to music that will shut your brain off to the white privilege that engulfs this country....BUY THIS FILM. Another thing that is so great about this eclectic barrage of white babies you can know that at least 20% of them are probably complete a-holes. Happy viewing.
Excellent for Memory Care.  Brought much joy and laughter.
